    "title": "[On February 24th \u2014 a day before the government named Mostaqur Rahman as governo...",
    "description": "[On February 24th \u2014 a day before the government named Mostaqur Rahman as governor of Bangladesh Bank \u2014 shares in Intech Limited climbed about 10 percent, from Tk 30 to Tk 33. A day after his appointment, the stock peaked at Tk 38.8, marking a further rise of roughly 17 percent. Since then, the share price has fallen back to Tk 32.9 as of March 4th.]",
